{"tid":2282280,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"主子沒落,跟班蓬佩奧一身蟻 被調查11宗失職","createTime":"2020-11-11T18:14:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-11T20:04:12.000Z","uid":73269,"like":3,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"1d4c641846f50f2c6d095e36f10b790a3d1b49e9","tid":2282280,"uid":73269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T18:14:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/1500p0/0x0/100/none/88787d4d130cb091491f908d8be0893d/stheadline/ST/Kolnews/2020/11/11/043921_jh2NYJhE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.stheadline.com%2Ff%2F1500p0%2F0x0%2F100%2Fnone%2F88787d4d130cb091491f908d8be0893d%2Fstheadline%2FST%2FKolnews%2F2020%2F11%2F11%2F043921_jh2NYJhE.jpg&h=18b40489&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://std.stheadline.com/kol/article/1731/%E6%94%BF%E5%95%86KOL-deepthroat-%E8%93%AC%E4%BD%A9%E5%A5%A7%E4%B8%80%E8%BA%AB%E8%9F%BB-%E5%8D%B8%E4%BB%BB%E5%BE%8C%E9%82%84%E8%A6%81%E9%9D%A2%E5%B0%8D%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Fkol%2Farticle%2F1731%2F%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%2595%2586KOL-deepthroat-%25E8%2593%25AC%25E4%25BD%25A9%25E5%25A5%25A7%25E4%25B8%2580%25E8%25BA%25AB%25E8%259F%25BB-%25E5%258D%25B8%25E4%25BB%25BB%25E5%25BE%258C%25E9%2582%2584%25E8%25A6%2581%25E9%259D%25A2%25E5%25B0%258D%25E8%25AA%25BF%25E6%259F%25A5&d=J6hOlXozLSF63%2FYIn%2B2AuzsyqOHkMMjDRpVYVMaq87A%3D&h=480dc809\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Fkol%2Farticle%2F1731%2F%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%2595%2586KOL-deepthroat-%25E8%2593%25AC%25E4%25BD%25A9%25E5%25A5%25A7%25E4%25B8%2580%25E8%25BA%25AB%25E8%259F%25BB-%25E5%258D%25B8%25E4%25BB%25BB%25E5%25BE%258C%25E9%2582%2584%25E8%25A6%2581%25E9%259D%25A2%25E5%25B0%258D%25E8%25AA%25BF%25E6%259F%25A5&h=628e85d3\" target=\"_blank\">https://std.stheadline.com/kol/article/1731/%E6%94%BF%E5%95%86KOL-deepthroat-%E8%93%AC%E4%BD%A9%E5%A5%A7%E4%B8%80%E8%BA%AB%E8%9F%BB-%E5%8D%B8%E4%BB%BB%E5%BE%8C%E9%82%84%E8%A6%81%E9%9D%A2%E5%B0%8D%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5</a><br />\n<br />\n紐約州民主黨眾議員、眾議院外交事務委員會（House Foreign Affairs Committee）主席恩格爾（Eliot Engel）稱，蓬佩奧拒絕接受調查人員的採訪，「我認為他是在試圖耗盡時間，避開調查人員，直到他離任。」蓬佩奧還拒絕接受就另一項重大調查進行的採訪，該調查涉及美國向沙特阿拉伯出售武器。<br />\n<br />\n屈指一算，連同上述五宗調查個案，蓬佩奧被調查的事件，已起碼有11宗，看來秋後算帳即將來臨，主子侵侵失勢沒落，其跟班蓬佩奧也難安枕。"},{"pid":"cb8da81d7d77916d72aac6e8e47fb6c9eb868b07","tid":2282280,"uid":73269,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T18:16:07.000Z","msg":"狗：你哋個肥奥要搵工"},{"pid":"d59fd872320ab9269b5893300fd2c51a38dced51","tid":2282280,"uid":52594,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T18:17:22.000Z","msg":"蓬佩奧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />前CIA Director"},{"pid":"829511e5656353224e648760326047c0e6d3ba69","tid":2282280,"uid":73269,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d59fd872320ab9269b5893300fd2c51a38dced51","tid":2282280,"uid":52594,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T18:17:22.000Z","msg":"蓬佩奧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />前CIA Director"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T18:19:18.000Z","msg":"這項調查涉及蓬佩奧與夫人在海外和國內的公務旅行"},{"pid":"f55d07f206da771c43f8c0597b697d6304dcd9d5","tid":2282280,"uid":306337,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T18:22:23.000Z","msg":"星島<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfed28fb876905699c5601be845d37575d358470","tid":2282280,"uid":73269,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f55d07f206da771c43f8c0597b697d6304dcd9d5","tid":2282280,"uid":306337,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T18:22:23.000Z","msg":"星島<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sos